snippet.title: Johnny Depp & Amber Heard Abuse Claims: Questions you should be asking (Part 2)
snippet.description:
In case you haven't watched Part 1 yet:  https://youtu.be/NfUvMF-kkXU
#johnnydepp #amberheard #metoo

Hey guys!  Thanks for being patient.  This has been an exhausting endeavor but one I feel to be very worth while.

This video picks up right where Part 1 left off.  So if you haven't seen that one, you might be a little lost if you go straight into this one.  I see Part 1 as more of a set up for Part 2...which I see as the grand finale.

Once again, this video may seem more speculative, but I base any of that in facts and sound reason.

Thanks again, and feel free to share and comment.  Take care!


Music: "Creative Minds" from bensound.com
